name: Arjun - Prince of Bali
description: Arjun - Prince of Bali is an Indian animated television series produced by Green Gold Animation. It premiered on 1 June 2014 on Disney Channel India. It is a spin-off of the show Chhota Bheem. The main character of the show, Arjun, was first featured in the film, Chhota Bheem and the Throne of Bali. The show features the adventures of Arjun, the prince of Bali.
